&lt;h3 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Installing it 
    &lt;div id=&#34;installing-it&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There are multiple ways to get it, be it from &lt;strong&gt;Arch&lt;/strong&gt; repos or &lt;strong&gt;Flathub&lt;/strong&gt;. I will be showing both methods, up to you to choose which you prefer&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;
